      "description": "CFD-predicted pressure head compared to FDA benchmark experimental measurements across 5 operating points. Mean absolute error 3.2% with 95% confidence interval derived from repeated experimental runs. Aleatory uncertainty from pump-to-pump manufacturing variation and measurement noise quantified via bootstrap resampling of n=12 experimental replicates.",
